description:
Subscribe to Vision Video for more faith-based movies and tv series: https://bit.ly/3LrbGIN

Courtney is a young African American girl who was trafficked for sex at age 17. Courtneys Story is a heart-wrenching story of a child from a broken home who went through many foster homes, but finally found stability in the home of a Christian couple. But, when her past life resurfaced, she plunged into a world of darkness that was almost impossible to escape.
